# Rule Precedence

When rules overlap, apply this precedence (highest first):

1. Explicit user instruction in the current session.
2. Safety/integrity rules (`engineering-rigor`).
3. Task completion gates (compile/format/test verification).
4. Domain style rules (`scala3`, `cats-effect`).
5. Operational convenience rules.
